name: Sunra LOGO | VIS Golden Ratio Grid
description:
I used Golden Ratio and Fibonacci Numbers to generate a series of circles, and make them into a grid. This Template can be used in icon design, prototype or animation design, etc.

Let's press "Like❤️" button. I will enlarge or update my design file anytime and you will see and duplicate it. No bad, right?


基於黃金分割比例設計，可用於 icon，LOGO，原型和動效等設計上。飛機稿。

按下“❤️”，我會隨時更新這個設計文件，也方便你隨時查看和複製，大家共同進步。
